{
    "json_version": 0x2,
    "name": "EVENT_MESSAGE_YY02_070.ebm",
    "nb_messages": 0x14,
    "messages": [
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "msg_string": "This goes like this, and this goes like this... Hmm, that's not right..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0xf,
            "name_id": 0xf,
            "extra_id": 0x11,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Are you having issues creating your recipe?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0xe,
            "name_id": 0xe,
            "extra_id": 0x11,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "If that's the case, do you want to talk again?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "Oh, sure. Maybe I will."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x30,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "Ah, that reminds me... You two know how Plachta was in the past, right?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x34,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "When Plachta was still human... What was she like?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0xe,
            "name_id": 0xe,
            "extra_id": 0xd,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "...Not much different than now. She was serious, and eager about research."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0xf,
            "name_id": 0xf,
            "extra_id": 0xd,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "She had a few loose screws, too... That still hasn't changed."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0xe,
            "name_id": 0xe,
            "extra_id": 0xf,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "That's right. Also, she had some strangely pure aspects to her."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0xf,
            "name_id": 0xf,
            "extra_id": 0xf,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "Indeed. She was always talking our ears off about how she wished to make people happy though alchemy."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "msg_string": "Huh..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0xe,
            "name_id": 0xe,
            "extra_id": 0x69,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "msg_string": "Well, regardless of that... As an alchemist, she was beyond top class."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0xf,
            "name_id": 0xf,
            "extra_id": 0x3c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xc,
            "msg_string": "Yes... Enough to make us envious."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xd,
            "msg_string": "Huh? Envious...?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0xe,
            "name_id": 0xe,
            "extra_id": 0x6b,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xe,
            "msg_string": "...Whoa. I think we talked a little too long."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0xf,
            "name_id": 0xf,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xf,
            "msg_string": "...Right. Sophie, was that enough for a change of pace?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x10,
            "msg_string": "Oh, y-yeah. Thanks."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0xe,
            "name_id": 0xe,
            "extra_id": 0x42,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x11,
            "msg_string": "That's good. We'll see you again."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2b,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x12,
            "msg_string": "(Did Luard start using Ablation Alchemy out of jealousy for Plachta's talents...?)"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2d,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x13,
            "msg_string": "(...Maybe I'm overthinking it.)"
        }
    ]
}